<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173302>
    bibo:endPage "60" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "43" ;
    bibo:volume "1275" ;
    dc:creator "Audisio, Paolo; Mancini, Emiliano; Biase, Alessio De" ;
    dc:date "2006" ;
    dc:title "A new species of the pollen­beetle genus Meligethes (Coleoptera: Nitidulidae) of the M. aeneus group from Greece, with review of the M. subaeneus complex" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173303>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173304>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173305>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173306> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173303>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Dorsal habitus of Meligethes epeirosi n. sp. (♂ paratype from Greece, Katara Pass, Fig. 1), of M. subaeneus Sturm (♂ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Fig. 2; ♂ specimen from Spain, Cantabria, Campollo, Fig. 3), and of M. matronalis Audisio & Spornraft (♂ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Fig. 4). Scale bar = 2.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173304>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 12. Tegmen and median lobe of aedeagus (dorsal view) of Meligethes coracinus Sturm (♂ specimen from Italy, Lombardia, Lovero Valtellino, Figs. 5 – 6), of M. subaeneus Sturm (♂ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Figs. 7 – 8), of M. matronalis Audisio & Spornraft (♂ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Figs. 9 – 10) and of Meligethes epeirosi n. sp. (♂ paratype from Greece, Katara Pass, Figs. 11 – 12). Scale bar = 0.50 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173304/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173305>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 16. Ovipositor of Meligethes coracinus Sturm (Ψ specimen from Italy, Lombardia, San Giacomo di Teglio, Fig. 13), of M. subaeneus Sturm (Ψ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Fig. 14), of M. matronalis Audisio & Spornraft (Ψ specimen from Italy, Latium, Rocca di Papa, Fig. 15) and of Meligethes epeirosi n. sp. (Ψ specimen from Greece, Katara Pass, Fig. 16). Scale bar = 0.50 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173305/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.173306>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Schematic drawings of morphological characters measurements for Meligethes species—a: body shape and pronotum; b: antennae; c: protibiae; d: protarsi; e: tegmen; f: aedeagus; g: aedeagal apex. Refer to Table 2 for list of characters and acronyms." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/173306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

